memberdef.name: READ_DATA
memberdef.initializer: switch(iDataType)\ {\ case AFDT_BYTE:\ READ_BYTE(data,int);\ break;\ case AFDT_SHORT:\ READ_SHORT(data);\ break;\ case AFDT_SHORT100:\ READ_SHORT(data);\ break;\ case AFDT_DWORD:\ READ_DWORD(data);\ break;\ case AFDT_FLOAT:\ READ_FLOAT(data);\ break;\ default:\ break;\ }

memberdef.name: READ_NULL_DATA
memberdef.initializer: switch(iDataType)\ {\ case AFDT_BYTE:\ rkStream.ReadByte();\ break;\ case AFDT_SHORT:\ case AFDT_SHORT100:\ rkStream.ReadShort();\ break;\ case AFDT_DWORD:\ rkStream.ReadDword();\ break;\ case AFDT_FLOAT:\ rkStream.ReadFloat();\ break;\ default:\ break;\ }

memberdef.name: READ_AddField
memberdef.initializer: if(!g_bWatch)\ {\ READ_DATA(iDataType,data);\ }\ else if(CompareVersion())\ {\ if(g_dwReplayVersion >= dwAddVersion)\ {\ READ_DATA(iDataType,data);\ }\ }\ else\ {\ if(RACE_CUR_VERSION >= dwAddVersion)\ {\ READ_DATA(iDataType,data);\ }\ else if(dwAddVersion > g_dwReplayVersion)\ {\ }\ else\ {\ READ_NULL_DATA(iDataType);\ }\ }

memberdef.name: READ_DelField
memberdef.initializer: if(!g_bWatch)\ {\ }\ else if(!CompareVersion())\ {\ if(g_dwReplayVersion >= dwDelVersion)\ {\ }\ else if(dwDelVersion > RACE_CUR_VERSION)\ {\ READ_DATA(iDataType,data);\ }\ else\ {\ READ_NULL_DATA(iDataType);\ }\ }\ else\ {\ if(dwDelVersion > g_dwReplayVersion)\ {\ READ_DATA(iDataType,data);\ }\ }
